# .env.supabase.example
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PulaTrack — Environment Configuration for Standalone Supabase Engine
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env.local` to override the Base44 configuration.

# Found under Project Settings -> API in your Supabase Workspace Dashboard
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-public-anon-key-here
